---
const books = [
  {
    title: 'Modern GPU Programming For MLSys',
    href: '/books/modern-gpu-programming-for-mlsys/',
    description: '面向机器学习系统的现代 GPU 编程中文翻译，包含章节正文、交互式示例和参考资料。',
  },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>yuancaoyaohw</title>
    <meta name="description" content="yuancaoyaohw 的电子书与博客入口" />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light dark;
        --bg: #f7f8fb;
        --text: #172033;
        --muted: #5c667a;
        --panel: #ffffff;
        --border: #d8dee9;
        --accent: #2457d6;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        :root {
          --bg: #111827;
          --text: #eef2ff;
          --muted: #a8b3cf;
          --panel: #182235;
          --border: #2c3954;
          --accent: #8fb3ff;
        }
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      main {
        width: min(1080px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 56px 0;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 60px);
        line-height: 1.08;
      }

      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 18px;
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      .intro {
        max-width: 760px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      .section {
        margin-top: 48px;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .card {
        display: flex;
        min-height: 190px;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 22px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--panel);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .card strong {
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 22px;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .card span {
        margin-top: 12px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .card em {
        margin-top: 22px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .links a {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>yuancaoyaohw</h1>
      <p class="intro">这里整理电子书、课程翻译和技术笔记。内容以可长期维护的文档站形式发布。</p>

      <section class="section" aria-labelledby="books-title">
        <h2 id="books-title">电子书</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          {
            books.map((book) => (
              <a class="card" href={book.href}>
                <span>
                  <strong>{book.title}</strong>
                  <span>{book.description}</span>
                </span>
                <em>打开</em>
              </a>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" aria-labelledby="more-title">
        <h2 id="more-title">更多</h2>
        <p class="intro">博客区会用于放置较短的技术文章、读书笔记和项目记录。</p>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="/blog/">博客</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/yuancaoyaoHW">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
